  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. A minor mesh-refinement revision was applied to the solver in late 2025; the primary experimental dataset predates that revision by approximately three weeks. The assessment narrative holds that the mesh change was not material to the dataset's relevance and therefore no formal re-validation against the revised model was performed.",
