      "name": "FDA Generic Centrifugal Pump — In-Vitro Hemolysis Experimental Dataset",
      "description": "In-vitro hemolysis index measurements collected across 5 flow-speed operating points using the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump geometry. Measurements were acquired prior to the mesh-refinement revision applied to the CFD solver. The assessment team concluded that the mesh change (a local near-wall refinement in the volute region) was not material to the experimental boundary conditions or the measured hemolysis values, and therefore the dataset was retained without re-collection or formal re-validation against the revised model build.",
      "dataVintage": "2025-10-24T00:00:00Z"
