      "description": "Inlet velocity profiles, outlet pressure boundary conditions, blood rheology parameters, and rotational speed settings for the 5 COU operating points. Compiled from device specification documents and clinical operating envelope data. Vintage post-dates the model revision.",
      "dataVintage": "2025-11-20T00:00:00Z"
    }
  ],
  "hasValidationResult": [
